(149, 1, 1, 573, 39, 562, NULL, 2, 'dernier avertissement', NULL, 'email_dernier_avertissement', 'Email dernier avertissement', NULL, 0, NULL, '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13px;\"=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: center; align-items: center; font-weight: bolder; text-transform: capitalize; list-style: none; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 7px;\">Email avec Accusé de réception</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13px;\"=\"\">A l\'attention de {{ DOSSIER_NOMCOMPLET }},</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13px;\"=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: center; align-items: center; font-weight: bolder; text-transform: capitalize; list-style: none; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 7px;\">Objet : dernier avertissement</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13px;\"=\"\">Nous sommes navrés de constater que nos précédents avertissements n’aient engagé aucun changement de votre part.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13px;\"=\"\">C’est pour cette raison que nous vous adressons une <span style=\"text-align: center; align-items: center; font-weight: bolder; text-transform: capitalize; list-style: none; padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 7px;\">lettre de dernier avertissement</span> à prendre en compte en pièce jointe.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13px;\"=\"\">Cette lettre vise à vous faire changer d’attitude. A défaut nous serons obligés de prendre à votre encontre des sanctions plus importantes.<br>C’est pourquoi nous vous invitons à faire le nécessaire pour un redressement immédiat et durable.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13px;\"=\"\">En vous souhaitant bonne réception,</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" segoe=\"\" ui\",=\"\" roboto,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" \"apple=\"\" color=\"\" emoji\",=\"\" \"segoe=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\";=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 13px;\"=\"\">Cordialement,<br>{{ DOSSIER_REFERENTPEDAGOGIQUE_NOMCOMPLET }}</p>', NULL, 0, '2024-10-31 15:22:31', '2025-01-31 10:10:46', 0, NULL, NULL),
