vention.</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 13px;\">Sans signature de votre part, nous devrons annuler notre proposition d\'intervention.<br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 13px;\">A très bientôt,<br>{{CIVILITE_RESPONSABLE_ECOLE}} {{NOM_RESPONSABLE_ECOLE}}<br>{{QUALITE_RESPONSABLE_ECOLE}}</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.625rem; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 13px;\">{{RAISON_SOCIALE_CENTRE}}<br>{{ADRESSE_CENTRE}} {{CP_CENTRE}} {{VILLE_CENTRE}}<br>{{TEL_CENTRE}} - {{EMAIL_CENTRE}} - {{SITE_WEB}}</p>', NULL, 0, '2024-10-31 17:02:38', '2024-10-31 17:03:27', 0, NULL, NULL);
